# EduAI-SA Product Requirements

## Product Name

EduAI-SA

---

# Mission

To give every learner a personal AI tutor and every teacher a personal AI assistant.

---

# Problem Statement

Many learners struggle to understand concepts because classrooms are large and teachers have limited time to provide one-on-one support.

Teachers spend significant time creating lesson plans, worksheets, memorandums, assessments, and reports.

Parents often want to support their children's learning but may not know how.

EduAI-SA exists to solve these challenges using artificial intelligence while keeping teachers at the centre of education.

